{"tid":460293,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"啊禮 唔好結婚。。。","createTime":"2017-11-06T13:43:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T17:35:24.000Z","uid":431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d8ba05d207a1fc99cb9b0ab662491414798c651b","tid":460293,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T13:43:29.000Z","msg":"佢有咩咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/214323_cc488e8dd1b389ac411e89d50107d294.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F214323_cc488e8dd1b389ac411e89d50107d294.jpg&h=1afb4d6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/214324_80856b2c42956b2acf47c6b4da0af376.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F214324_80856b2c42956b2acf47c6b4da0af376.jpg&h=77072d79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0ce3723426e3cd01e40688c04e12ad99373718e","tid":460293,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T13:43:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢有咩咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/214323_cc488e8dd1b389ac411e89d50107d294.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F214323_cc488e8dd1b389ac411e89d50107d294.jpg&h=1afb4d6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/214324_80856b2c42956b2acf47c6b4da0af376.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F214324_80856b2c42956b2acf47c6b4da0af376.jpg&h=77072d79&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我覺得個頭開得唔錯 我嗰時有幾個角色都覺得有做反角嘅可能性 但我對哩套戲嘅唔好印象大於好印象<br />\n<br />\n1. 吳彥祖嗰part個人觀感有啲隔硬嚟 甚至覺得有啲多餘 個感覺係導演淨係想用香港啲高樓大廈玩吓災難性層層疊 之後就特登安排佢講個計劃名出嚟咁 有啲唔係好知哩part做乜撚咁<br />\n<br />\n2. 父囡情條線打得唔夠入 感動位覺得有啲尷尬<br />\n<br />\n3. 反角個犯事理由太撚唔合理呱 想炸咗全世界之後做個美國總統 做乜鳩？跟住又係俾人捉到就做5分鐘解說點解佢要犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘩屌 娘到一個點<br />\n<br />\n4. 雖然知佢係美國電影 但哩套嘅大美國英雄主義 同埋過份歌頌美國嘅情懷 真係有啲嘔心 尤其最後嗰句咩 「因為老子就是美國總統！」WTF<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然係馬後炮 但如果個故事變成美國總統真係背後策劃人 為權力而表面做好人 但暗中搵人阻止男主角 整幾條伏線指向其他角色屈鳩佢哋做反角 而女主角同女船長係總統後後嘅間諜咁 可能會好睇啲<br />\n<br />\nsor 可能太認真 但我真心覺得佢曬咗個idea"},{"pid":"c80c89ea89e895e938b72921b9655d4584e1a743","tid":460293,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T13:44:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14839d24d82f5843020b436cf73fd47a4006557e","tid":460293,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T13:47:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢有咩咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/214323_cc488e8dd1b389ac411e89d50107d294.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F214323_cc488e8dd1b389ac411e89d50107d294.jpg&h=1afb4d6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/214324_80856b2c42956b2acf47c6b4da0af376.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F214324_80856b2c42956b2acf47c6b4da0af376.jpg&h=77072d79&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我覺得個頭開得唔錯 我嗰時有幾個角色都覺得有做反角嘅可能性 但我對哩套戲嘅唔好印象大於好印象<br />\n<br />\n1. 吳彥祖嗰part個人觀感有啲隔硬嚟 甚至覺得有啲多餘 個感覺係導演淨係想用香港啲高樓大廈玩吓災難性層層疊 之後就特登安排佢講個計劃名出嚟咁 有啲唔係好知哩part做乜撚咁<br />\n<br />\n2. 父囡情條線打得唔夠入 感動位覺得有啲尷尬<br />\n<br />\n3. 反角個犯事理由太撚唔合理呱 想炸咗全世界之後做個美國總統 做乜鳩？跟住又係俾人捉到就做5分鐘解說點解佢要犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘩屌 娘到一個點<br />\n<br />\n4. 雖然知佢係美國電影 但哩套嘅大美國英雄主義 同埋過份歌頌美國嘅情懷 真係有啲嘔心 尤其最後嗰句咩 「因為老子就是美國總統！」WTF<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然係馬後炮 但如果個故事變成美國總統真係背後策劃人 為權力而表面做好人 